#. type: Plain text
#: ../wiki/en/Running-a-Server.md:104
msgid "#### Running in Registered mode"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../wiki/en/Running-a-Server.md:106
msgid "The following minimum setup is required to [run a Registered Server](Running-a-Server#server-types):"
